These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
4 different games are played: monopoly, canasta, chess, snooker
City: hamburg, prague, venice, rome
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, malaysian, colombian, mexican
House: townhouse, tower, modern, wooden
 1. the malaysian is not to the right of the japanese##8
 2. the townhouse house is not to the left of the townhouse house##8
 3. the wooden house is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the japanese is not to the left of the mexican##8
 5. the townhouse house is not to the right of the townhouse house##8
 6. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the mexican##1
 7. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the right of the person playing monopoly##5
 8. the person traveling to rome is between the tower house and the malaysian##2
 9. the wooden house is the person traveling to venice##1
10. the wooden house is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
11. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the person traveling to hamburg##3
12. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the right of the person playing canasta##5
13. the person traveling to venice is not to the left of the wooden house##8
14. the person playing canasta is the modern house##1
15. the person playing canasta is not the malaysian##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Game         | monopoly     | canasta   | snooker | chess |
| City   | prague | rome   | hamburg   | venice  |
| Nationality         | malaysian  | colombian  | mexican  | japanese |
| House     | townhouse    | modern | tower     | wooden    |

