.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, azalea, balloon-flower, daisy
House: palace, farmhouse, victorian, wooden
City: nizza, edinburgh, colone, paris
The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, designer, social-worker, doctor
 1. the person traveling to colone is between the project-manager and the person traveling to edinburgh##2
 2. the person who growsazalea is not to the right of the designer##8
 3. the person who growsazalea is on the left or right of the palace house##3
 4. the person who growsiris is not to the right of the doctor##8
 5. the project-manager is not to the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##8
 6. the wooden house is not to the right of the person who growsdaisy##8
 7. the social-worker is somewhere to the left of the doctor##5
 8. the social-worker is in an odd position##4
 9. the person traveling to nizza is the designer##1
10. the person traveling to colone is on the left or right of the project-manager##3
11. the project-manager is not to the left of the person traveling to colone##8
12. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
13. the person traveling to paris is somewhere to the right of the farmhouse house##5
14. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left or right of the person traveling to colone##3
15. the person who growsiris is on the far left or far right##3
16. the victorian house is on the right of the palace house##1
17. the person who growsiris is not to the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##8
18. the farmhouse house is not to the right of the designer##8
19. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the farmhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
