.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-3::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, car, scooter, tram
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, soy-milk, 7up, milk
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, june, october, january
4 different games are played: poker, snooker, domino, monopoly
 1. the person playing poker is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
 2. the person driving the car is somewhere to the right of the person driving the scooter##5
 3. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the left of the person drinking milk##5
 4. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in may##5
 5. the person playing domino is not to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##8
 6. the person driving the tram is not to the left of the person drinking 7up##8
 7. the person who's birthday is in october is in an odd position##4
 8. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 9. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
10. the person playing snooker is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking almond-milk is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##8
12. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Transport         | bus    | tram   | scooter | car |
| Beverage   | almond-milk     | 7up  | milk   | soy-milk      |
| Birthday   | june | may    | october      | january       |
| Game         | domino    | poker | monopoly   | snooker    |

