There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, black, grey, ebony
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, martial-arts, adventure, fantasy
 1. the person who growsiris is not the person who likes purple##6
 2. the person who likes ebony is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies##3
 3. the person drinking cola is the person who likes grey##1
 4. the person drinking coffee is between the person who likes purple and the person who likes black##2
 5. the person who growsiris is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3
 6. the person watching scientific movies is not to the right of the person drinking coffee##8
 7. the person who growsballoon-flower is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who growsiris is somewhere to the right of the person who growszinnia##5
 9. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
10. the person who likes black is the person watching scientific movies##1
11. the person watching martial-arts movies is not to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##8
12. the person who likes purple is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
13. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
14. the person who likes black is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
15. the person who growszinnia is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
