The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, november, may, july
There 4 different types of food: orange, grapes, zucchini, potato
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, lemonade, cola, water
 1. the person who's birthday is in october is not to the left of the bluemaster-smoker##8
 2. the person eating potato is the bongani-smoker##1
 3. the person drinking lemonade is not the bluemaster-smoker##6
 4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in october is not to the right of the person eating zucchini##8
 6. the person drinking cola is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in october##8
 7. the person drinking lemonade is not to the left of the bongani-smoker##8
 8. the person eating grapes is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 9. the person eating orange is not to the left of the tiparillo-smoker##8
10. the person who's birthday is in may is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##8
11. the person drinking water is between the tiparillo-smoker and the person who's birthday is in november##2
12. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
13. the person eating grapes is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in november##8
14. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Cigar         | tiparillo     | bluemaster | ritmeester   | bongani  |
