 6. the person who's sport is tennis is not to the right of the person who growslily##8
 7. the person who's sport is sailing is not the person who growsdaisy##6
 8. the person traveling to paris is somewhere between the person who likes green and the person who's sport is sailing##7
 9. the person who likes green is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to paris##5
10. the person who likes azure is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3
11. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
12. the person traveling to paris is not the person who growspoppy##6
13. the person who growslily is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is sailing##5
14. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
