 5. the person playing bridge is in an even position##4
 6. the owner of the rat is somewhere between the person playing canasta and the person playing whist##7
 7. the owner of the rat is not to the left of the owner of the hamster##8
 8. the owner of the pony is somewhere between the person who likes grey and the person who likes white##7
 9. the person who growssunflower is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person who growsaconite is not to the left of the person who growsaconite##8
11. the person who growssunflower is on the far left##1
12. the person who growsiris is on the far right##1
13. the owner of the rat is the person who likes grey##1
14. the person who likes grey is not to the left of the person playing whist##8
15. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the right of the person playing poker##5
16. the person who growsaconite is not to the left of the person who likes red##8

