.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |     3     |    4    |
| Transport           | roller | jet-ski       | boat      | subway  |
| House   | palace    | colonial | modern   | craftsman   |
| Cigar   | vegafina   | montecristo          | siglo      | swisher  |
| Beverage   | tea   | water      | juice | lemonade |

